{"tid":1155673,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟4】總部拍攝原址曝光　防劇透拍完即還原剩返一道門","createTime":"2019-05-15T05:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T09:42:12.000Z","uid":66923,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"56c51b69f8d670e4c43734d7afd53092bd1fce20","tid":1155673,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"Marvel Studio 10週年鉅作《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）上映數週，熱潮不退，繼續有很多有關劇情、後續和週邊新聞引起大家的關注，而一眾演員亦紛紛在社交網站上傳拍攝時的花絮和幕後照片，相信除了他們也跟粉絲同樣不捨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xyt52RV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxyt52RV.jpg&h=6c73f3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「復仇者聯盟」總部又大又靚，擁有各種高科技機器，卻慘被「魁隆」一下子炸成灰燼。（《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》劇照）<br />\n<br />\n近日在社交網站上提及了《復仇者聯盟4》的總部，指出真身原來是中國一家企業，名為「三一集團」（SANY），而該集團是中國最大、全球第五的工程機械製造商，也是全球最大的混凝土機械製造商，同時美國總部設在美國東南部佐治亞州的Peachtree城。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYptgcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYptgcf.jpg&h=674fb40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有觀眾入場看完《復仇者聯盟4》在網絡上表示《復仇者聯盟4》的總部竟然似層相識，原來是她一早已經去過拍攝現場，並寫下感想︰「&hellip;&hellip;忽然想起去年六月，我和周老師（冒着酷暑）去佐治亞州的Peachtree城採訪中國三一重工的美國總部。公司負責人神秘地說，工廠剛剛借給《復聯》拍完電影，簽了保密協議，拍完後工廠一切復原，只留下了這個門。結果發現，電影室內實景基本都在三一的車間裡拍的，我看的時候一直在想，這不是他們停挖土機的地方嗎！這不是他們員工打羽毛球的地方嗎！我的觀後感太獨特了&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0WWp54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0WWp54.jpg&h=576b66d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據知「三一集團」借出拍攝後已經還原本來樣貌，不過就留底這扇門，粉絲又知道是哪一幕嗎？（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URHiDrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURHiDrC.jpg&h=6c207326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GHR3Pyh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGHR3Pyh.jpg&h=11960a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCr3Pyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCr3Pyi.jpg&h=953e1ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdT52Uf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdT52Uf.png&h=a92213ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKDRdZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKDRdZY.jpg&h=323e1bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xoX6NjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxoX6NjZ.png&h=afe66054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ntp5irF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtp5irF.png&h=b96e618c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVBSHTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVBSHTm.png&h=906fbdf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEhRYrG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEhRYrG.png&h=03d9bf62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s06vuyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs06vuyn.png&h=ddd645f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gn7JTRUT894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgn7JTRUT894&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=ecdd0dec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gn7JTRUT894</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.do/eSqZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.do%2FeSqZY&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=84cc056a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.do/eSqZY</a>"},{"pid":"ab4d0474a6a01a8e4a363e62ead8c2bbcf1987eb","tid":1155673,"uid":193642,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"有咩原因令一間中國企業係美國設廠?"},{"pid":"af843b72eddd2dbe3aa581d64983235b78b18dd0","tid":1155673,"uid":53498,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"c